data.title: EU Login
data.text:
Please note:

By clicking on any of the links, you will leave the website of the European Commission and be redirected to the website of the respective Sign-in Service.

Any subsequent transfer of data from you to the Sign-in Service is subject exclusively to that Sign-in Service's terms of use and privacy policy and outside of the European Commission's responsibility. It is recommended to read those terms and policies before you use the Sign-in Service and grant the necessary permissions.

In case of successful sign-in, the European Commission receives an e-mail identifier of the authenticated identity from the Sign-in Service, confirming the successful sign-in. For more details on EU Login processing please read the Privacy Statement below.
